import { Card, Container, Typography, Divider, Grid, IconButton } from '@material-ui/core'
import DeleteIcon from '@material-ui/icons/Delete'
import EditIcon from '@material-ui/icons/Edit'
import useStyles from './styles'

const EditCard = ({ employee }) => {
    const classes = useStyles()

    return (
        <Card className={classes.editCard}>
            <Container className={classes.cardFrontTop}>
                <Typography>{employee.firstName} {employee.lastName}</Typography>
                <Divider className={classes.divider}/>
            </Container>
            <Grid container direction="column" justify="center" alignItems="center" xs={12}>
                <IconButton>
                    <EditIcon />
                </IconButton>
                <IconButton>
                    <DeleteIcon />
                </IconButton>
            </Grid>
        </Card>
    )
}

export default EditCard
